            -> there can be at most 16 groups of size >=3 
            -> first make all groups size <=2 or make total size==20
            -> if all groups are of size<=2, there exist a strategy to 
                just delete n-20 character and not letting any new group form 
                'by unintentional merging'.
            -> then do the req. char insertions by replacement
        */

