The key idea is to get maximum number of set bits starting from the leftmost bit. I've used mask to keep the prefix of every number.

mask after each iteration:
```
10000000000000000...
11000000000000000...
11100000000000000...
11110000000000000...
11111000000000000...
11111100000000000...
